	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello all,
<br />
<br />I'm getting lots of totally _awesome_ stuff done with my FPGA-based NES.  I will post an update to my website soon.  But in the interim I was hoping you guys could help me find a game.  I have a feeling that it D.N.E. but I'm looking for a mapper 0 game that utilizes the Save-RAM space ($6000-7FFF).  Any help?  I'd like to have it so I can run some tests on my existing hardware. Thanks in advance!!
<br />
<br />Pz!
<br />
<br />Jonathon <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

